WRITING.TEXT: Played a ton of Wildlands, my feedback thus far: Really liked the opening, the environment and enemies look really appealing. Controls are good and I don #8217;t mind the closer camera. Gunplay is great, nice and tight. Graphics aren #8217;t bad at all, great colours and wind effects in the foliage looks great. Driving the bikes seems off, doesn #8217;t have the sense of speed that Wildlands did? Not a fan of the new menu and gunsmith, seems really clunky... and no more hold Y to holster your gun?? Very turned off that my biggest pet peeve from Wildlands has returned... the ****ing shoulder swap. I don #8217;t know if it #8217;s just me but I find the cover system really frustrating sometimes, can #8217;t get my character to swap sides when I want, and always get stuck over my left shoulder which for whatever reason is infuriating haha I know you can hit RB to swap back but I remember this being an issue for me in Wildlands. Not major, just annoying. The boys will be on tomorrow for some co op, maybe make another post with the thoughts of the group. Thanks for the beta!
